<h1 id="unified-posting-date-control" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="30">Unified posting date control</h1>

[!include[banner](../includes/banner.md)]
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">This topic explains how to configure chronology control of invoices posting dates within a specific sales tax book section.</p>
<h2 id="prerequisites" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="37">Prerequisites</h2>
<ul sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">The primary address of the legal entity must be in Italy.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Italian sales tax books and sections are configured in the system. For more information, see <a href="emea-ita-fiscal-books.html" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Italian sales tax books</a>.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">In the Feature management workspace, turn on the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">(Italy) Unified posting date control</strong> feature. For more information, see <a href="../../fin-ops-core/fin-ops/get-started/feature-management/feature-management-overview.md" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Feature management overview</a>.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="configure-posting-date-control" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Configure posting date control</h2>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Complete the following steps to configure posting date control.</p>
<ol sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Go to <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Tax</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Sales tax</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Italian sales tax book sections</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">In the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Skip posting date control</strong> column, select whether posting date control is required for a selected sales tax book section.</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49"><img src="media/emea-ita-post-date-control.jpg" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49" alt="Posting date control."></p>
<ul sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">If the field isn't enabled, which is the default option, the system doesn't allow posting of new invoices with dates earlier than the date of the latest posted invoice.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-ita-post-date-control.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">If the field is enabled, the system allows posting with any date.</li>
</ul>
